than raising money?

27:38.700 --> 27:41.007
I'd pony up for that.

27:41.050 --> 27:45.272
♪

27:45.315 --> 27:47.535
- I mean, of course I'm glad
he was so sincere,

27:47.578 --> 27:50.407
but I shouldn't be
so easily swayed by an apology.

27:50.451 --> 27:52.540
