in and you're my boss' boss?

28:12.081 --> 28:14.910
- No, because I've been
married four times,

28:14.954 --> 28:18.871
and after each divorce, I swore
I'd never do it again.

28:18.914 --> 28:21.134
- Yes, but you did.

28:21.177 --> 28:23.005
- Yeah, I did.

28:23.049 --> 28:25.051
- Why?

28:25.094 --> 28:28.402
- Because ignoring my feelings
didn't make them go away.

28:28.445 --> 28:31.971
So I decided
to ignore my fears.

28:32.014 --> 28:34.016
Katy and I have been together
for nine years.

28:34.060 --> 28:35.626
- Hmm.

28:35.670 --> 28:39.892
- So I say run towards love.
You'll never regret it.

28:39.935 --> 28:41.545
♪

28:41.589 --> 28:43.504
- ♪ I'll take you there

28:43.547 --> 28:46.246
- ♪ Ooh, I know a place

