together...right?

33:40.409 --> 33:42.150
They don't--they don't have
to think about it

33:42.194 --> 33:44.065
or ever even stop
and ask why.

33:44.109 --> 33:45.893
They just are.

33:45.936 --> 33:48.156
But you know what is so
super-duper special

33:48.200 --> 33:49.810
about our family?

33:49.853 --> 33:51.942
- What?

33:51.986 --> 33:55.207
- We chose each other.

33:55.250 --> 33:57.383
I chose you.

33:57.426 --> 33:59.124
♪

33:59.167 --> 34:01.909
[voice breaking] I chose
your brothers and your sister.

34:01.952 --> 34:05.086
♪

34:05.130 --> 34:08.176
And I just wouldn't want it
any other way.

34:08.220 --> 34:09.786
♪

34:09.830 --> 34:11.875
- Me either.

34:11.919 --> 34:14.139
♪

34:14.182 --> 34:17.098
- So I'm--I'm gonna stop
feeling sorry for myself

34:17.142 --> 34:19.927
[sniffles] I'm gonna stop
feeling sad for me and you,

34:19.970 --> 34:22.103
and I'm gonna feel sad
for Grandma and Grandpa,

34:22.147 --> 34:26.542
because they are choosing
to miss out on all of us.

34:26.586 --> 34:28.066
♪

34:28.109 --> 34:30.546
All right?

34:30.590 --> 34:32.287
Okay?

34:32.331 --> 34:34.942
♪

34:34.985 --> 34:36.813
I love you, kiddo.

34:36.857 --> 34:38.772
♪

34:38.815 --> 34:40.426
- I love you.
