38:15.641 --> 38:22.561
♪

38:22.604 --> 38:25.172
- I am so sorry I have been
unavailable all night,

38:25.215 --> 38:28.567
but I am here now,
and I am ready to charm you.

38:28.610 --> 38:31.396
- Don't bother.

38:31.439 --> 38:33.528
- Certainly saves me
some time.

38:33.572 --> 38:35.313
[chuckles]

38:35.356 --> 38:38.185
- Every year the
medical director corners me,

38:38.228 --> 38:41.014
charms me, says whatever
they can to get me

38:41.057 --> 38:43.495
